**Retest Status: Not Fixed**

During retesting, it was observed that although credit card information is no longer displayed, a crew member user without the required permissions can still access the Payment Methods page through forceful browsing/direct URL access and view billing-related information.

The root cause of the issue is missing server-side authorization controls. The remediation implemented only removes specific data from the page but does not prevent unauthorized users from accessing the functionality.

To fully remediate this issue, server-side access controls should be enforced to ensure users without the necessary permissions cannot access the Payment Methods page or its associated information.
