During retesting, the issue was verified and no invalid digital certificate was observed in the Production (PROD) environment at the time of assessment. The behavior appears to be limited to the UAT environment as per current validation.

Based on the available evidence during retest, the issue is not impacting the production environment. However, it is recommended to ensure certificate configurations remain consistent across environments to avoid potential misconfiguration risks during deployment.

